<br>
I've been thinking one of the big problems with getting our crown: getting to the 7th isle and staying long enough to clear it enough times for everyone to get one.  I'm currently saving for my crown, but would rather get it myself.<br>
<br>
I devised a plan which if executed should allow mages on your server to get their crown anytime they can muster the force to clear the 7th isle (2 - 3 groups).  This uses the standard summon corpse bridge used in so may sky raids to create an &quot;anchor&quot;.  So any raid can skip all the way to the 7th isle any time the anchor is available.<br>
<br>
This plan involves getting access to a  planes capable toon which can summon corpse (51 SK, 46 necro) and another which can revive (46 paladin or cleric).  Summon corpse toon should be bound in the bazaar.  You need exclusive access to these two toons for a few weeks at least, hopefully forever.  A small coffin corpse summoner isn't really necessary since you can always bring one later.  If you are able to camp a small coffin corpse summoner then use the appropriate sized coffins in the appropriate steps.<br>
<br>
This plan has two parts:<br>
<br>
PART I - Parking the toons<br>
<br>
Required:<br>
- 2 sky stones<br>
- 4 large coffins<br>
- 4 small coffins<br>
- A donation (optional)<br>
- Mage summoned chokers (optional) - Saves on coffins/sky stones<br>
<br>
Its a good idea to have both toons have at least one of each coffin.  Who holds the extras doesn't matter (they aren't for your use anyway)<br>
<br>
Get someone to park both toons on the first isle at anytime using your first sky stone.  Camp them and log them in periodically until you find people on the 7th island with 2 clerics, 1 wizard and a summon corpse capable toon who has at least one coffin of the appropriate type on them already.  This may take a while.<br>
<br>
Have the wizard invite 1st cleric (cleric1) and summoner into the group.  Have the wizard and cleric1 stay close together, summoner move out of port range.  Wizard casts Alter: Plane of Sky to port back to zone in.  <br>
<br>
Have wizard group your two toons.  Hand wizard a sky stone to replace the one he just used.  Duel and revive any characters going to the 7th isle.  That could be all 4 of you, or just two of you if the raid is breaking up and cleric1 and the wizard are going to jump anyway.  Don't duel close to any mobs.  The Efreeti in the quest room and Sirran will &quot;assist&quot; people being attacked.<br>
<br>
Give each character being summoned the appropriate sized coffin.  Since you don't know when first porting up what kind of summoner will be available you have 4 of both kinds.  Have necro summon each person, and cleric2 revive them again.  As each person arrives, hand the coffin to their summoner to replace the one it just used.<br>
<br>
Now would be the time to give your donation.  You are now ready to camp and come back and restart the 7th isle anytime you want.  Just make sure you know if/when your helpers are leaving so you don't butt heads.  They may be staying for another clearing.<br>
<br>
PART II - Restarting your raid<br>
<br>
Arrange before hand to have the wizard of the raid be in the bazaar with one coffin for your summoner to use.  This will allow your summoner to bring up his summoner (hopefully a small coffin summoner).  Being in the Bazaar, you can bank any fees.  Have the wizard invite your summoner into his group.  Your rezzer now revives your summoner and is back in sky on the 7th isle.  During this operation have the rezzer watch the corpse.  If its going to expire soon (it expires in several minutes from a duel) rez back the summoner and try again if necessary.<br>
<br>
*WARNING* The time the summoner spends not on the PoA is the one time that you could totally mess up your setup.  If for some reason the summoner can't be rezed back before the corpse expires, he'll have to pay to get back into Sky, summon his own corpse and wait until the next sky raid to get back on to the 7th island.<br>
<br>
Okay, so now you have a wizard who is the leader of a group.  Your summoner is back on the 7th isle.  If anyone goes LD, its not a problem, just repeat the previous step.  Have the wizard invite their summoner into the group.  Have their summoner duel, be rezzed to produce a corpse.  Your summoner summons theirs and your rezzer revives them.<br>
<br>
Next up is their rezzer.  Once their rezzer and their summoner is on the island you are done.  Both of your toons can disband and camp.  If you are going to bring up a raid yourself always make sure you don't operate at a coffin deficit.  Each extra summon/rez you do that person should have a coffin of the appropriate size on them.<br>
<br>
Even if you end up being the main summoner, as soon as you can you camp.  Although the island is non-agro better safe than sorry.  As long as you have access to those two characters you can do this as often as you like.  The cost of bringing up a raid isn't too bad.  They only use as many coffins as they have people plus as many sky stones they need to port themselves up, plus any fees you may charge.<br>
<br>
If you need to switch out toons:<br>
Have your summoner do the duel, get invited by wizard, get coffin, get rez thing.  Then wizard can port up the replacement, along with a rezzer, duel, rez, summon, rez the replacement.  Everyone else jumps off.  Cost 1 sky stone, 1 coffin.<br>
<br>
Make sure anyone using reagents uses a mage summoned choker.  Nothing like saving money on a sky stone or coffin.<br>
<br>
I think every mage community on every server should have this setup.<br>
<br>
I'm working to set it up on Tarew Marr.  I have a 47+ rezzer already.  Just need access to a corpse summoner. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uizarek.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Izarek</A> at: 7/17/02 4:52:02 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ukrilenspiritlink.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Krilen Spiritlink</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 176<br> <font color=#333333>(7/17/02 4:33:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlibrarysubmissions.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=104.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Restarting a 7th isle Plane of Sky raid at any time</span><hr size=1> Duh. People usually refer to this as a necro bridge, i believe. People also exploit it to bring more than 24 people on teh raid.<br>
