<br>
Also if a guild is starting their Sky raid the same time you are on the 7th island, its not likely to be a problem.  It takes 2-3 days to get there anyway.<br>
<br>
Also clearing the 7th island isn't likely to cause a problem for people.  If you haven't done the previous island and spawned the big bad mob on this island, you won't be able to spawn Sirran.  That would be the one thing that could screw up an existing raid because if Sirran is spawned on one island he can't be spawned on another.  But the way the 7th island is done its not possible if you just port up to 7th island.<br>
