<br>
An alternative to the necro bridge strategy is upon making it to island 7, one necro leaves a corpse up there with all keys on it.  After raid is over they head back up to air and summon corpse to Island 1.  Once per week, necro heads up to air, loots corpse and dies again.  This keep a corpse with all 7 keys on island 1 ready to go.<br>
<br>
To start raid, necro runs up through the islands, getting to Island 7.  Given how few islands have agro, and how few mobs see invis this run is fairly quick and easy.<br>
<br>
Once on island 7, they summon their group members using the normal duel, die, revive method.  If you don't have a pally, cleric alt to do the first summons you can even use a soul crystal.<br>
